{"tid":39423,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［非故］頭先㩒㩒下電話差啲變蜘蛛俠","createTime":"2016-12-14T14:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T14:55:47.000Z","uid":13717,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"004c259331a7ce33abe973bec179ebd7773594b8","tid":39423,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:26:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的 呢件事發生係五分鐘之前<br />\n咁阿甲我呢就係澳洲讀緊書<br />\n澳洲細細粒甲由都可以成隻牛龜咁大隻都見怪不怪<br />\n但係蜘蛛呢 恐怖就算身為連登仔嘅我 我最驚嘅生物之一（？）<br />\n話就都準備瞓教架啦 熄晒燈 諗住係張床㩒多陣電話就瞓架啦<br />\n覆覆下女神 唔知點解feel到好似有條頭髮跌左落塊面<br />\n咁大家肯定有同感嘅就係 有條頭髮係塊面到係超唔舒服嘅事<br />\n你反射反應唔理係乜你都會拎開佢架啦<br />\n點知想拎走條「頭髮」果陣 我揸落去果下個手感<br />\n嗯？ 點解唔係一條嘅？而係好大嘅一粒 <br />\n之後太黑睇唔到 用電話照下啦<br />\n以下係我嘅反應<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母 蜘蛛</span></span><br />\n但係呢 我竟然冇嗌到出黎 我直接起身 好冷靜咁拎起旁邊嘅廁紙<br />\n將佢放係張紙巾到<br />\n佢反反肚 同佢好似有眼神交流咁<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一下<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">噗吱</span></span>一聲就送左佢上路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我掉左張紙巾落垃圾桶 頭也不回<br />\n呢一刻 我覺得喂屌你老母 隻手指公痛痛地咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4cc3992d14d73890bd0b416bd971416c7852db","tid":39423,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i2.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/000/675/096/e2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Fnewsfeed%2F000%2F675%2F096%2Fe2a.jpg&h=f15dedf8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e2effbb43ec9717117a5b4700e5e6dfb63cab0","tid":39423,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:32:26.000Z","msg":"What I became<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/gGruZGY4Gvk/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FgGruZGY4Gvk%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=78be63e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86fec3bf3fb63ee22c3119668451547c8a65ca1b","tid":39423,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:33:15.000Z","msg":"聽講十連又會有人衝入黎阻止我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1"},{"pid":"68621e18e7ceea478a71cf0a355275543da8e75b","tid":39423,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:33:26.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"35ecc4e8e25cbd37237f2488576a68ca51fec818","tid":39423,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:33:55.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"5cb290960c61e20aadc2bd2135f545e127cc6006","tid":39423,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:34:06.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"0eaa069cda3d399756afa51dde46f984e8aff00b","tid":39423,"uid":41656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a7fc444efcebfea3ad221a3270613de4a3231c","tid":39423,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:34:38.000Z","msg":"斷鳩樓主屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負評我比嘅<br />\n成撚日懶好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clow