lyTime":"2016-12-14T14:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日一定會更加開心啫 你話係咪呀"},{"pid":"4b3c248807040ca35e7500cab8d48ec3d8332103","tid":39423,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:46:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都唔知做乜撚 成日上黎係到博存在感 自己屌自己 好撚幽默咩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀係呀我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}